Race.SpecificTitle: Sewerage District No. 2 -- 16.98 Mills Renewal - BOC - 10 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall the Caddo Sewerage District No. 2 of the Parish of Caddo, State of Louisiana (the "District"), continue to levy and collect 16.98 mills tax on all the property subject to taxation in said District (an estimated $96,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with year 2019 and ending with the year 2028, for the purpose of paying the maintenance and operating expenses of sewerage collection and disposal in the District?
